text: Mililani is a city located near the center of the island of Oahu in Honolulu County, Hawai ªi, United States. It is made up of two census-designated places, Mililani Town, with a population of 28,121 at the 2020 census, and Mililani Mauka, with a 2020 census population of 21,075. ==References== Category:Settlements in Hawaii
